      About this item

      • 355 Pan/Tilt & Human TrackingThis camera can rotate 355 horizontally and 140 vertically to cover every angle and leave no blind spot. It could auto tracking the moving person, so it would not miss any human motion events.
      • 2.5K HD & Color Night Vision4MP resolution camera with super HD image allows you to clearly see every detail of your surveillance on the Zosi Smart app. It supports optional color 100ft night vision, allowing you to see more details day or night to keep more of your favorite things safe.
      • Person Vehicle Detection & Real-time AlertsZOSI smart camera has AI detection, it can more accurately detec people, cars, pets, and packages, and you can custom the alerts specific areas to reduce unnecessary notifications. The camera can react with sound and light when human motion is detected, and you will receive instant app push notification and email alert.
      • Two-Way Audio & Remote AccessBuilt-in mic and speaker let you stay in touch with your household. Remote access and control anytime anywhere you want. Check in with the family or tell your dog to stop barking, or say hello through the ZOSI Smart App.
      • 24/7 Recording & 2TB Hard DriveSupport Ultra-Long Continuous Recording and Backup By USB. It can be set to automatically overwrite the oldest internally stored footage or you can transfer video files by USB to a memory stick or external hard drive. The Plug-in WiFi cameras connect wirelessly to a NVR(Only supports 2.4GHz WiFi). Please note both the WiFi security cameras and the NVR require the power connection. Additionally, the NVR requird an Ethernet cable connect to router.

                  How customer reviews and ratings work

                  Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

                  To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

                    5.0 out of 5 stars A Really Feature Packed Wireless PTZ Camera & NVR System
                    Reviewed in the United States on March 1, 2024
                    Amazon Vine Customer Review of Free Product( What's this? )
                    In my system I located the NVR within an outdoor enclosure mounted on a pole. Power and CAT6 cable that is connected to the Gateway device are within the enclosure. To facilitate NVR administration a USB and HDMI are hardware adapted and run over CAT5 to the indoors where a PC is connected to the USB & HDMI adapters outputs.
                    A Really Feature Packed Wireless PTZ Camera & NVR System

                    The footprint of the NVR is very small allowing for convenient placement.

                    In my system I located the NVR within an outdoor enclosure mounted on a pole. Power and CAT6 cable that is connected to the Gateway device are within the enclosure. To facilitate NVR administration a USB and HDMI are hardware adapted and run over CAT5 to the indoors where a PC is connected to the USB & HDMI adapters outputs.

                    I then located the four wireless camera's to their new locations to fill in some holes in my existing camera network.

                    The NVR is very well featured, providing granular control over a wide host of functions which are what make this system exceptional.
                    The native operating voltage of the NVR & camera's is 12Vdc.

                    * Granular control over PTZ pre-set is done on a per camera basis.
                    * Configuration of Email in the event of any alarms is straight forward.
                    * The Record settings: per camera configuration for video quality, & Time Stamp.
                    * Schedule: configure Motion Detection, Intelligent Detect per camera.
                    * Alarm: configure for Motion Detect, Video Loss, Intelligent Detect, & Siren Light/Alarm

                    - The NVR offers far more settings beyond what I have mentioned!

                    The default username and password are "admin" & the password field is lefty empty, be sure to modify your password once logged into the Zosi GUI of the NVR within "Users".

                    I have had this system in now for almost a month and I am pleased with it's WiFI connectivity reliability. Image quality in both night and day are sharp and clear with exceptional detail and clarity, night vision quality too is solid. Camera connection to the NVR is very easy out of the box, upon powering of each camera the NVR will automatically search and pair with the camera. Adding new cameras requires that you follow the detailed pairing options. The system AI does very, very well in distinguishing human vs animal movement, I have dogs within our yard which is fenced, sometimes cat's, possum or racoon may come in from the forest, detection of human movement vs animal is accurate!
                    I spent some time tweaking the settings to come up with really shocking accuracy with respect to the AI detection.
                    This system coming with the 2TB HDD provides ample video storage as well, when necessary exporting video or still captures is easy.
                    Being able to expand this system to 8 cameras is a big plus!

                    - The spot-light does a pretty good job, the light is brighter than I expected!

                    This NVR & Camera system are a winner and very well worth the small amount to purchase it!

                    * As a note; You will need to purchase 4 new 12Vdc power transformers to power the cameras.
                    I then located the four wireless camera's to their new locations to fill in some holes in my existing camera network.
